Package Framework

Interface Summary
IDisplayObject The IDisplayObject instance contains all the data for displaying something by an ICore instance.
IInput IInput implementations access input from Env3D.
IWorld IWorld implementations provide the virtual world functionality for the simulation.
 

Class Summary
Core Core is intended to provide the core functionality for the top-level aquarium simulation class.
DisplayObject The DisplayObject contains all the data for displaying something by a Core instance.
